Package: otpr
Title: An R wrapper for OpenTripPlanner
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Marcus", "Young", email = "M.A.Young@soton.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: An R wrapper for OpenTripPlanner (OTP) <http://www.opentripplanner.org/>.
    OTP is an open source platform for multi-modal and multi-agency
    journey planning written in Java. OTP provides a REST API which otpr uses to query OTP.
